    "description": "玛丽亚是一位自由的女性，绝对已经达到任何国家的合法饮酒年龄。<br>她穿着兔子装参加了一场假面舞会派对。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/7dfe771a441aeebd9a724bfc7ad70685.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/7dfe771a441aeebd9a724bfc7ad70685.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/7dfe771a441aeebd9a724bfc7ad70685.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>维塔利碰巧也在同一个俱乐部，他注意到了她，并主动提出请她喝一杯好喝的饮品。<br>由于未知原因，玛丽亚失去了意识。而维塔利，作为一个真正的绅士，将她柔软的身体放进后备箱，带到他的乡村住宅，好让她休息得更好。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>醒来后，玛丽亚意识到维塔利把她带到了自己的地方。但她不是那种人。因此，她坚决决定无论如何都要逃离这里……<br><strong>而且要免费！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我们该怎么办？</h2><br>你需要驾驶一辆豪华银色哈弗，从维塔利的乡村住宅偷偷逃走。<br>解锁门锁、砸开木板、打开配电箱、砸坏地板、扔碗盘，用嘈杂的声音吸引维塔利的注意，并享受PS4时代的画面效果！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏的主要特点：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要逃离这个邪恶住宅的物品位置是随机的！<br></li><li>一个神秘的追求者，无论你藏在哪里，他都会追着你。<br></li><li>一个充满魅力的女主角，让人无法抗拒。<br></li><li>计划有多个逃生路线。最终会实现的。<br></li><li>大量的彩蛋！<br></li><li>真正的镜中反射！你上次看到这种效果是什么时候？<br></li><li>你可以躲在马桶里。<br></li><li>变得成功又富有！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/193c8458f3a8628c372e3acf32701c1d.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/193c8458f3a8628c372e3acf32701c1d.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/193c8458f3a8628c372e3acf32701c1d.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
